<MudText Typo="Typo.h3">How To Comfirm your Email</MudText>
<MudGrid>
    <MudItem xs="12" sm="4">
        If the mail is not in the spam filter, you need to check the "Speciel spam filter" called "quarantine".
        You find it by follow the next link <MudLink Href="https://security.microsoft.com/quarantine" Target="_blank">https://security.microsoft.com/quarantine</MudLink>.
        Sign in with your KU-mail, and go to the next step in this guide.
    </MudItem>
    <MudItem xs="6" sm="4">
        <MudImage Fluid="true" Src="/Guids/3.png" Class="rounded-lg"> </MudImage>
    </MudItem>
    <MudItem xs="6" sm="4">
        <MudImage Fluid="true" Src="/Guids/4.png" Class="rounded-lg"> </MudImage>
    </MudItem>
    <MudItem xs="12">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h6"> Step:1</MudText>
    </MudItem>
    <MudItem xs="12" sm="4">
        Now you have come to the microsoft quarantine, click on the mail from noreply@kuliv.dk.
        <MudField Variant="Variant.Outlined" Label="Note:">
            Note the "Release Messege" do not always work, so go to the next step in this guide insted.
        </MudField>
        <MudField Variant="Variant.Outlined" Label="Note:">
            It can take a little time to loade the side, so if you still haven't received an email with a code, write an email from your KU email to <MudLink Href="mailto:Support@kuliv.dk">Support@kuliv.dk</MudLink> and we will manual comfirme your account.
        </MudField>
    </MudItem>
    <MudItem xs="12" sm="8">
        <MudImage Fluid="true" Src="/Guids/5.png" Class="rounded-lg"> </MudImage>
    </MudItem>
    <MudItem xs="12">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h6"> Step:2</MudText>
    </MudItem>

    <MudItem xs="12" sm="4">
        Now press the "Preview Messege" if its not there, try click on <MudIcon Icon="@Icons.Filled.MoreHoriz"></MudIcon>
        and it will give you more options.
    </MudItem>
    <MudItem xs="12" sm="8">
        <MudImage Fluid="true" Src="/Guids/6.png" Class="rounded-lg"> </MudImage>
    </MudItem>
    <MudItem xs="12">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h6"> Step:3</MudText>
    </MudItem>

    <MudItem xs="12" sm="4">
        Now you almost there just copy the code in to KULiv.dk.
    </MudItem>
    <MudItem xs="12" sm="8">
        <MudImage Fluid="true" Src="/Guids/7.png" Class="rounded-lg"> </MudImage>
    </MudItem>
    <MudItem xs="12">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h6"> Step:4</MudText>
    </MudItem>

    <MudItem xs="12">
        If you still haven't received an email with a code, write an email from your KU email to <MudLink Href="mailto:Support@kuliv.dk">Support@kuliv.dk</MudLink> and we will manual comfirme your account.
    </MudItem>
</MudGrid>


